<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA611_01_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema611_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema611_01_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2 flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
          <span class="title_text" lang="y">『수학 3-2』 분수 알아보기</span>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1_brown" lang="y">색칠한 부분을 분수로 나타내어 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center gap_30">
          <div class="img_area box1">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA611_01_IH/0001_01.png" alt="" />
            <div class="input_position">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <div class="input_wrap hint_right">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="3" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap hint_right">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="8" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="img_area box2">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA611_01_IH/0001_02.png" alt="" />
            <div class="input_position flex align_center gap_10">
              <div class="input_wrap hint_up">
                <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
              </div>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <div class="input_wrap hint_right">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="5" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap hint_right">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="6" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div lang="y" class="fraction_text">
                  색칠한 부분은 전체를 똑같이 8로 나눈 것 중의 3이므로
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>3</span>
                    <span>8</span> </span
                  >입니다.
                </div>
                <div lang="y" class="fraction_text">
                  색칠한 부분은 1과 전체를 똑같이 6으로 나눈 것중의 5이므로 1<span class="fraction_box ml_0">
                    <span>5</span>
                    <span>6</span> </span
                  >입니다.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
